.TH LIGHTNING-CHANNEL-BOTH-BALANCES-VARIANCE 1
.SH NAME
lightning-channel-both-balances-variance \- variance of both local and remote balances across channels
.SH SYNOPSIS
lightning channel-both-balances-variance
.SH DESCRIPTION
Reports the variance of combined local and remote balances in millisatoshis.
.SH OUTPUT
JSON object with key both_balances_variance_msat.
